{"type":null,"faqId":38956,"title":"如何切换手环的屏幕界面？","answer":"<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.9111111in 1.25in 1.0in 1.25in;}\n.p1{text-indent:0.29166666in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:0.29166666in;margin-left:0.5833333in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:0.5833333in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;}\n.p4{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:14pt;}\n.p5{text-indent:0.25in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.11111111in;}\n.s2{font-weight:bold;}\n</style>\n<div>\n<p>\n<span>切换手环屏幕界面有2种方法：</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>手环支持触屏操作，滑动屏幕进行切换。手环默认显示时间主界面，上下滑动即可查看步数、卡路里、睡眠等界面。</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=126630\" style=\"width:1.3625in;height:2.3909721in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"></p>\n<p>\n<span class=\"s1\">2.  </span><span>翻腕切屏。1）手环戴在手腕上，手腕保持水平。2）点亮手环屏幕。3）较快速转动手腕大约90度，手腕保持水平，即可切换屏幕。</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=126631\" style=\"width:1.575in;height:2.3in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"></p>\n<p class=\"p5\"></p>\n</div>","faqTypeId":212,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"4266","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1441673016000,"seriesProductName":"B0-Honor","visitedTimes":48,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}